{"tid":708443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：愛的侏羅紀　恐龍哥接機𠱁細妹","createTime":"2018-06-19T10:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T10:19:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"675b90d5a9965de2e608af8eaccde6665339e56a","tid":708443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180619/20424554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F20424554&d=IYB1KEC4QVtgI8ppafVNdpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=66497173\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F20424554&h=96b12ae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180619/20424554</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月19日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：愛的侏羅紀　恐龍哥接機𠱁細妹<br />\n<br />\n3,599<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n最近有一套以恐龍為題材嘅電影上映，片中嘅恐龍被人捉咗出大都市&hellip;&hellip;噚日朝早有一隻「恐龍」張牙舞爪出現喺香港國際機場接機大堂，金睛火眼望住出閘嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n讀者劉先生昨早準備同家人出發外遊，喺接機大堂A出口見到有一隻恐龍雙手扶着欄杆，頭岳岳喺閘外望穿秋水。冇幾耐一個女仔同爸爸媽媽出嚟，一見到恐龍就大喊：「哥哥！」而恐龍哥哥亦回應話：「阿妹，我等咗你好耐！」阿妹見到恐龍哥哥，忍唔住興奮跳起，又摸吓頭握吓手仲攬到實一實，四萬咁口影相留念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180619/large/a1203b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180619%2Flarge%2Fa1203b.gif&h=2d1457cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■由爸媽傍住嘅妹妹，一出閘就認出「阿哥」，興奮上前擁抱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉先生估計阿妹出國一段時間，所以哥哥先着起恐龍模型服𠱁佢開心，仲等阿妹安頓好先至換返衫，原來恐龍哥哥真身係一個戴眼鏡、打扮斯文嘅男仔。劉生睇見呢一幕好感動，指通常男仔對女友先會咁花心思，估唔到恐龍哥哥為妹妹一樣落足心機，仲覺得自己好幸運可以見到呢個溫馨和平嘅場面，「好sweet，希望社會可以多啲愛！」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：屈原咆哮端午前氾濫　城門河淹單車徑<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：警民擒茶壺賊　㩒地半粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7187ca62efecd63d730dca6a3b76cee87e30f8a1","tid":708443,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"妹妹似係肥妹仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}